      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "The 2YOs kick us off and THE SPEED MACHINE (3) looks the one to beat. The Hanseatic gelding has shown sharp speed in two jump-out wins and gets Holder for his debut. LALOR (1) was well backed on debut but faded late after doing the work in front. Can go one better with that run under his belt. WHITE POINTER (4) has trialled up nicely for the Hickmott yard and with Toeroek from the inside draw he should make his presence felt. CZECH OUT (2) wasn't far away here on debut in December and looks to have taken the next step after a solid jump out. Looks to have found a tough race but can fill a drum. VANDAROSS (5) next.",
